          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this property to create or look up other Metal resources that use the same device as your SceneKit renderer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "This property is valid only for scene renderers whose "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnscenerenderer/1522616-renderingapi"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " value is "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnrenderingapi/scnrenderingapimetal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ". You create a SceneKit view that renders using Metal with the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnpreferredrenderingapikey"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " initialization option or in Interface Builder, or an "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnrenderer"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " that uses Metal with the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnrenderer/1518404-rendererwithdevice"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " method. For OpenGL-based scene renderers, this property’s value is always "
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "nil"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
